Distribution . This species is widely distributed in the Oriental and Australian Regions. It has been recorded from China , Taiwan ( Mazzoldi 1995 ); the Philippines ( Ochs 1924 ;
Freitag et al. 2016
); Japan ( Takizawa 1931 ); Indonesia ( Ochs 1949 , 1953 ): Java , Bali , Lombok, Sumba, Sulawesi , Buru; New Guinea ( Ochs 1955 ), Australia ( Ochs 1949 ; Watts & Hamon 2010 ); New Caledonia ( Satô 1966 ; Mazzoldi 2010 ); and the Pacific Islands: Vanuatu ( Watts & Hamon 2010 ) and Fiji ( Ochs 1949 ). This is the first time it has been recorded in Thailand .
